hods other than simple majority are used for\npairwise elections. We investigate some natural definitions of \"close to tied\"\nfor general functions and exhibit an example where the distribution over\ntournaments is not uniform under those definitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2018 04:09:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 00:16:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2020 00:41:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-27"}
