wer-bound of $2$ was conjectured to be tight by Hartline and\nRoughgarden (2009) and Alaei et al.\\ (2015). We acquire a better lower-bound of\n$2.15$, and thus disprove this conjecture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2018 13:24:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2020 18:43:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-23"}
