ld vary from a gas giant planet on a circular orbit at a few AU\nfrom the central star to a brown dwarf on an eccentric, wide orbit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2018 15:07:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-18"}
